Meanwhile, detectives in Nyeri are following crucial leads that could help unravel the abduction of a Nyeri businessman by unknown people. Gerald Giandaru was kidnapped 10 meters from his barbershop. Two more people were abducted in Kieni west along the Nyeri Nyahururu highway on Wednesday evening, just a day after gerald was kidnapped in what is now turning out to be a worrying trend in the area.
